  "name": "Directed Audience",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>You can shape the area of your composition spells. Whenever you cast a composition spell whose area is an emanation, you can change the spell's area to a cone 10 feet larger, to a maximum of twice the original area.</p>\n<p>For example, you could modify a composition spell that affects a @Template[type:emanation|distance:30] to affect a @Template[type:cone|distance:40], but a @Template[type:emanation|distance:5] could only become a @Template[type:cone|distance:10].</p>"
